data.description: This is home located in the village of Theresa with incredibly affordable municipal electricity. PLEASE NOTE: This property is NOT in a flood zone. The metal roof is only 5 years old. This home offers a main floor bedroom and 2 more bedrooms upstairs with a full upstairs bathroom. The downstairs bathroom has been completely redone, with fully tiled flooring and shower, and the washer and dryer are located here as an added convenience. The expansive living area has a pellet stove as a secondary heat source when you want that toasty winter evening for snuggling up with a good book. The is a large dining area that leads into the kitchen that has a good-sized pantry space. The mudroom has been built on the side entrance for storage of all your seasonal gear.  The enclosed front porch is just waiting for your rocking chairs. The garage has been converted to a downstairs shop and storage space and upstairs is an open space with a full bathroom and heat, perfect for additional guests! You also have over 40 ft on the Indian River with gorgeous views all year long. There is a trail nearby that offers access to your waterfrontage on the river. Grab your kayak and make an appointment to tour!
